\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8216\'91Cant give that, you won\u8217\'92t have anything to hold up your hair.\u8217\'92}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8216\'91Oh no, what will I ever do.\u8217\'92}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Seculla, pressentation matters.}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Tis a new style. Pella, I just gave that woman ease of life for a year. All it cost me was the pain of having my hair touching my shoulders.}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Pella takes off her comb and gives it to seculla.}
